overview: The newest entry in the Badazz Filmz Universe, we are proud to introduce to you The Waterboyz. Directed and written by Tone the Goat, we follow the tale of urban youths in the city just trying to turn water into money. This is through and through a coming-of-age story with a modern twist. Follow The Waterboyz through good times and times that make them grow as people and a unit. This is Badazz Film’z first production not directly written by Boosie Badazz himself, and we intend to present other filmz and media from outside sources in the future as well. So, if you believe you have what it takes to bear the Badazz moniker and you know how to contact us, get at us and let’s make it happen.
title: Waterboyz
